      • calculateShortestDistanceBetweenVertexes

        java.lang.Integer calculateShortestDistanceBetweenVertexes(T firstVertex,
                                                           T secondVertex)
                                                    throws NoSuchVertexException
        Counts the shortest distance between two vertexes (considers each vertex of the same length)
        Parameters:
        firstVertex - id of a first vertex
        secondVertex - id of a second vertex
        Returns:
        if there is a path from firstVertex to secondVertex returns distance between them otherwise 2147483647 (2^31 - 1)
        Throws:
        NoSuchVertexException
